WEBVTT

00:00:29.739 --> 00:00:32.519
A ona je rekla: "Fenomenalno."

00:00:32.519 --> 00:00:34.754
Pomislila sam: "Stvarno?!"

00:00:34.754 --> 00:00:37.376
Fenomenalno ili tek dovoljno dobro

00:00:37.376 --> 00:00:42.040
što smo odlučili ponovno 
posjetiti vaš restoran?"

00:00:42.040 --> 00:00:44.400
Neki dan, jedan od mojih 
suradnika pitao me

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:46.880
mogu li nešto spremiti 
u PDF-formatu.

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:50.621
Rekla sam: "Pa, naravno." 
A on na to: "Fenomenalno!"

00:00:50.621 --> 00:00:56.848
Ozbiljno... Može li 
spremanje bilo čega u PDF-u

00:00:56.848 --> 00:00:59.796
biti fenomenalno?!

00:00:59.796 --> 00:01:02.956
Nažalost, česta pretjerana 
uporaba riječi "fenomenalno"